{"tid":721982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"日本晉級球迷失控　大阪道頓堀爆人造地震","createTime":"2018-06-29T06:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T14:59:07.000Z","uid":10338,"like":334,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"e2074d487afb30590df6dc01897afb862c400746","tid":721982,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:12:00.000Z","msg":"「藍武士」戲劇性打入16強，日本多地出現球迷失控，完全無視警察勸阻，造成大阪道頓堀戎橋，出現近乎地震似的搖動，連在場参與者都大呼恐怖。 <br />\n<br />\n一如以往，戎橋賽後又塞滿大批球迷，人數是上場對塞內加爾的两倍，橋上根本完全無法通行。人們大叫大跳，連橋呈現搖晃，有人驚叫「恐怖」、「地震聲音一樣」，但球迷依然忘形慶祝。比賽結束後三十分鐘，出現了第一個人跳河祝捷，然後有超過三十人有樣學樣，對大阪府警樹立的「跳河危險」、「請勿跳河」告示視若無睹。 <br />\n<br />\n東京澀谷車站路口同樣聚集大量球迷，即使警察努力控制交通，並用擴音器呼籲「危險！請慢慢跟隨前者過馬路」，在場Fans依然到處亂跑。只是不少人樂極生悲，丢失銀包、手機者眾，弄得警方要在車站前設立臨時報失接待處。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/141144_3de0d9b32a295d3dde9150f044a5215f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F141144_3de0d9b32a295d3dde9150f044a5215f.png&h=a2a33e1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77a33abced7d0e4e5a4e8a0c883f48558768bddc","tid":721982,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf4aa2f3c67760a987afb2d71ee635e10aaa09d","tid":721982,"uid":95413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7a21fcb0f75cf6a8abda0f557e33d42e7916f5","tid":721982,"uid":103207,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japa